column5: Mornin everyone, gonna be another sunny & warm one, hope y'all  have a great day
Morning Lew....  Off to work for me...  You have a good day too...
G'marnin' all . . . .   holidays this week, looks like a perfect day to chase some pike downtown!
Morning everyone, yeah, 24C here today. Anyone thinking ice fishing?
Hey all, I managed to sleep in today, have a great one all...  Maureen

....G'day all, been out for a while (puppy training ya know). Georgeous out there and sure wish I was going to be fishing but I'm going to take advantage of the weather and do some window caulking and painting.
